1
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:37,810
[A Forbidden Marriage]

2
00:01:38,990 --> 00:01:40,920
[Episode 24]

3
00:01:42,410 --> 00:01:46,979
[Seclusion Valley]

4
00:02:43,990 --> 00:02:46,250
There's a mark on your hand, Sect Leader.

5
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:52,280
Is that something you should be asking?

6
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:55,360
After everything that's happened,

7
00:02:55,740 --> 00:02:58,740
you actually still want
to make up with Shengyue Sect.

8
00:03:00,190 --> 00:03:00,840
Qing,

9
00:03:02,030 --> 00:03:03,890
you've disappointed me greatly.

10
00:03:06,250 --> 00:03:08,050
Is it that I've disappointed you

11
00:03:09,150 --> 00:03:12,360
or that you have been affected
by Biluo Valley's Six Harmonies Divine Art

12
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:14,020
and now take orders from them?

13
00:03:16,340 --> 00:03:18,540
Biluo Valley has sinister intentions.

14
00:03:18,730 --> 00:03:20,280
The missing children case in Yangliu Town

15
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,520
was Biluo Valley's doing.

16
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:25,380
What happened in Yunyin Village
was also pinned on us by Biluo Valley.

17
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,760
I just never imagined

18
00:03:32,030 --> 00:03:35,750
that you'd stoop to colluding with them.

19
00:03:38,810 --> 00:03:39,750
Nonsense.

20
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,140
Stop making wild guesses.

21
00:03:48,829 --> 00:03:50,160
The mark on your hand...

22
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,000
is fading.

23
00:03:54,329 --> 00:03:56,130
What mark are you talking about?

24
00:03:57,650 --> 00:03:59,800
Lu Jin has been practicing
the Six Harmonies Divine Art.

25
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,200
Those struck by his palms

26
00:04:01,470 --> 00:04:03,070
will have a mark left on them.

27
00:04:04,610 --> 00:04:05,940
When the mark festers,

28
00:04:07,140 --> 00:04:08,470
bones rot and pus flows,

29
00:04:09,220 --> 00:04:10,880
leading to a miserable death.

30
00:04:11,740 --> 00:04:13,740
But you haven't shown any symptoms.

31
00:04:14,270 --> 00:04:17,130
Instead, the mark is barely visible.

32
00:04:18,630 --> 00:04:21,760
You've been bewitched
by that witch from Shengyue Sect,

33
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,900
and now you're talking nonsense.

34
00:04:25,220 --> 00:04:25,630
Fine,

35
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,780
I'll help you come to your senses.

36
00:04:29,510 --> 00:04:31,870
Stay in there and reflect on yourself!

37
00:04:45,210 --> 00:04:47,130
[Saintess Hall]

38
00:04:47,130 --> 00:04:50,000
What?
The Shengyue Token is the Moon Blade?

39
00:04:50,180 --> 00:04:51,040
Yuan Yingxing,

40
00:04:51,420 --> 00:04:52,590
are you kidding me?

41
00:04:53,430 --> 00:04:54,750
Yao Fu said she's sick

42
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:57,300
and she needs both the Sun and Moon Blades
to cure her illness.

43
00:04:57,300 --> 00:04:58,060
You actually believe

44
00:04:58,060 --> 00:04:58,690
such a lie?

45
00:05:00,700 --> 00:05:03,100
I think she's truly clouded your judgment.

46
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:04,180
Lingyin said

47
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,730
she'll die soon.

48
00:05:06,860 --> 00:05:08,520
She's always full of schemes.

49
00:05:08,860 --> 00:05:10,260
If she really needs them,

50
00:05:10,530 --> 00:05:11,990
why doesn't she come get them herself?

51
00:05:11,990 --> 00:05:14,790
Why does she keep trying
to sow discord between us?

52
00:05:14,890 --> 00:05:15,750
Yuan Yingxing,

53
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,520
how many times has this happened?

54
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:19,160
Why do you always choose to believe her

55
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,230
instead of me?

56
00:05:21,070 --> 00:05:21,630
Yue,

57
00:05:22,310 --> 00:05:23,420
that is not a lie.

58
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:27,220
She said that
after taking Lingyin's Compliance Pill.

59
00:05:27,390 --> 00:05:28,800
She stayed with me before

60
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,680
and married Yang Qing

61
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:33,400
just to get both the Sun and Moon Blades.

62
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:34,159
Fine.

63
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,730
Even if all this is true,

64
00:05:37,310 --> 00:05:39,110
is it really worth it for someone

65
00:05:39,290 --> 00:05:40,110
like her?

66
00:05:40,830 --> 00:05:42,950
Why should we care
whether she lives or dies?

67
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:43,950
She killed me once

68
00:05:44,630 --> 00:05:46,480
and has deceived you countless times.

69
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:49,040
Is giving up the Sun and Moon Blades
for someone like her

70
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:49,570
worth it?

71
00:05:51,390 --> 00:05:53,920
Worth it or not,
what difference does it make?

72
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:56,540
I can't just stand by and lose her.

73
00:05:57,500 --> 00:05:59,500
If something happened to Yang Qing,

74
00:05:59,750 --> 00:06:01,210
would you act the same way?

75
00:06:01,460 --> 00:06:03,480
Don't you dare compare her to Yang Qing.

76
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,480
She's not worthy.

77
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:13,130
Have you really made up your mind?

78
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:16,010
The Sun Blade is
the Alliance Leader's Token.

79
00:06:16,300 --> 00:06:18,850
The Moon Blade is the Shengyue Token
symbolizing the status

80
00:06:18,850 --> 00:06:19,980
of our sect's chief.

81
00:06:20,290 --> 00:06:21,620
Something so precious—

82
00:06:22,510 --> 00:06:24,440
you really want to give them to her?

83
00:06:29,060 --> 00:06:29,720
As you said,

84
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:31,760
it's just a symbol of status,

85
00:06:31,780 --> 00:06:33,380
without much practical use.

86
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:36,270
We might as well use it to save a life.

87
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,880
Since when do you care about human life?

88
00:06:38,980 --> 00:06:40,580
Yue, tell me,

89
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:43,050
what will it take for you to help me?

90
00:06:46,340 --> 00:06:49,480
The Sun Blade belongs to Yunmen after all.

91
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:53,159
Yang Qing only entrusted it to me
temporarily.

92
00:06:53,950 --> 00:06:55,480
If something goes wrong...

93
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,120
If something goes wrong,

94
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:59,159
I'll take full responsibility.

95
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:02,830
Is she really that important to you,

96
00:07:03,060 --> 00:07:05,060
more important than Shengyue Sect?

97
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:07,040
If Shengyue Sect is gone,

98
00:07:07,300 --> 00:07:08,360
I could rebuild it.

99
00:07:09,570 --> 00:07:10,570
But without her,

100
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,920
I don't know what I would become.

101
00:07:31,970 --> 00:07:32,650
Thank you,

102
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:33,600
Yue.

103
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:42,740
You said

104
00:07:43,460 --> 00:07:45,920
the Sun and Moon Blades
could save your life.

105
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:52,990
What are you thinking about?

106
00:07:55,310 --> 00:07:55,830
I...

107
00:07:57,060 --> 00:07:58,320
Since you've got them,

108
00:07:58,390 --> 00:07:59,450
hurry up and leave.

109
00:07:59,690 --> 00:08:01,820
Don't stay here and bother me anymore.

110
00:08:04,990 --> 00:08:05,850
Yuan Yingxing.

111
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,049
Why is it you?

112
00:08:37,700 --> 00:08:40,150
I've already given you
the Sun Blade and Moon Blade.

113
00:08:40,150 --> 00:08:41,480
What are you doing here?

114
00:08:41,549 --> 00:08:42,880
Do you have a death wish?

115
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:43,360
I...

116
00:08:46,670 --> 00:08:48,270
I can stay for a few more days.

117
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:51,670
How unfortunate for you,

118
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:54,880
having to live like this
for a few more days.

119
00:08:55,270 --> 00:08:56,630
That's not what I meant.

120
00:09:11,270 --> 00:09:12,530
What are you doing now?

121
00:09:16,270 --> 00:09:18,030
I don't have what you want now,

122
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:21,260
so you don't need to pander to me anymore.

123
00:09:27,150 --> 00:09:27,750
Yingxing,

124
00:09:29,510 --> 00:09:30,120
do you still remember

125
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,360
how we first met?

126
00:09:32,630 --> 00:09:35,690
You were bathing in the hot spring
in the back mountain.

127
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:39,460
I pretended to sneak into Shengyue Sect
to get your attention.

128
00:09:39,870 --> 00:09:40,530
Yes,

129
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:43,950
and I actually fell for it.

130
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:47,680
I thought you were a spy from Yunmen

131
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:49,320
and wanted to tease you a bit,

132
00:09:49,610 --> 00:09:50,940
but little did I know...

133
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,450
I'm sorry.

134
00:09:55,450 --> 00:09:57,310
I shouldn't have let my obsession

135
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,660
lead me to hurt your feelings.

136
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:03,160
What's the point of saying all this now?

137
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:04,820
Don't expect to get my forgiveness

138
00:10:04,820 --> 00:10:05,820
before you leave.

139
00:10:07,870 --> 00:10:08,610
Yingxing,

140
00:10:10,180 --> 00:10:11,440
I'm not saying all this

141
00:10:13,060 --> 00:10:14,700
to get your forgiveness.

142
00:10:17,290 --> 00:10:18,570
I just want to tell you

143
00:10:20,450 --> 00:10:21,380
that I love you.

144
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:27,050
What did you say?

145
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:28,300
I said

146
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:30,770
I love you.

147
00:10:31,700 --> 00:10:33,610
Actually, I've loved you for a long time,

148
00:10:33,610 --> 00:10:35,010
but for various reasons,

149
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,280
I couldn't tell you,

150
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:39,450
nor was I able to express it.

151
00:10:40,710 --> 00:10:41,500
Yesterday,

152
00:10:42,580 --> 00:10:44,780
after thinking about it for a long time,

153
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:47,810
I still felt
I needed to tell you how I feel.

154
00:10:48,970 --> 00:10:51,970
If this troubles you,

155
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:55,080
just be troubled for a few more days.

156
00:10:56,150 --> 00:10:57,390
For the next few days,

157
00:10:58,510 --> 00:10:59,810
let's get along well,

158
00:11:00,490 --> 00:11:01,180
okay?

159
00:11:17,370 --> 00:11:18,570
You said it yourself.

160
00:11:19,210 --> 00:11:20,360
During the next few days,

161
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:22,160
we must be together at all times.

162
00:11:32,940 --> 00:11:35,910
[Seclusion Valley]

163
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:51,950
Mr. Yang.

164
00:11:55,150 --> 00:11:56,880
As long as you agree to marry me,

165
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:59,530
Sect Leader Feng will surely release you.

166
00:12:03,650 --> 00:12:05,380
I've already married Wangyue.

167
00:12:05,910 --> 00:12:07,170
I will never marry you.

168
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,210
You can divorce her.

169
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:14,000
Do you really want
to stay here in darkness

170
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:15,400
for the rest of your life?

171
00:12:19,420 --> 00:12:21,070
Thank you for your kindness, Miss Lu.

172
00:12:21,070 --> 00:12:22,020
I appreciate it.

173
00:12:22,940 --> 00:12:24,200
However, in this life,

174
00:12:24,680 --> 00:12:26,280
Wangyue will be my only wife.

175
00:12:27,870 --> 00:12:30,000
Wang Yue is a witch from Shengyue Sect.

176
00:12:30,940 --> 00:12:32,370
What's so good about her?

177
00:12:35,070 --> 00:12:36,430
How am I inferior to her?

178
00:12:38,670 --> 00:12:39,800
No matter who she is,

179
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,270
she is my wife.

180
00:12:44,910 --> 00:12:45,910
Fine, Yang Qing.

181
00:12:48,380 --> 00:12:49,510
Then I'll be direct.

182
00:12:51,370 --> 00:12:53,200
Biluo Valley will soon lead all the sects

183
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:55,800
to besiege Mount Yin
and attack Shengyue Sect.

184
00:12:56,820 --> 00:12:59,420
By that time,
I will kill that witch personally

185
00:12:59,890 --> 00:13:01,560
and bring her head before you.

186
00:13:03,560 --> 00:13:04,480
If she dies,

187
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:08,060
let's see
how you can remain faithful to her.

188
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:28,170
Junior Yang.

189
00:13:29,580 --> 00:13:30,310
Senior Wang.

190
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:33,250
Are you alright?

191
00:13:33,390 --> 00:13:34,000
I'm fine.

192
00:13:35,350 --> 00:13:37,140
The sect leader
has been acting strangely lately.

193
00:13:37,140 --> 00:13:38,700
He's actually taking orders from Lu Jin.

194
00:13:38,700 --> 00:13:39,960
Something must be wrong.

195
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:40,790
You need to leave quickly

196
00:13:40,790 --> 00:13:42,170
and investigate this matter.

197
00:13:42,170 --> 00:13:43,150
We can't allow Yunmen

198
00:13:43,150 --> 00:13:44,750
to become a pawn of Biluo Valley.

199
00:13:44,750 --> 00:13:45,600
But what about the sect leader?

200
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:46,910
Don't worry about that.

201
00:13:46,910 --> 00:13:47,710
I have my ways.

202
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:48,560
By the way,

203
00:13:48,650 --> 00:13:49,870
I've told Jiang Yan and Shang Huai

204
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:50,630
to wait for you
at the foot of the mountain.

205
00:13:50,630 --> 00:13:51,690
Take them with you,

206
00:13:51,870 --> 00:13:53,760
so you can look after each other
on the journey.

207
00:13:53,760 --> 00:13:54,910
If you let me go like this,

208
00:13:54,910 --> 00:13:56,040
what if the sect leader blames you?

209
00:13:56,040 --> 00:13:56,810
Don't worry.

210
00:13:57,210 --> 00:13:59,740
Yun and I owe you a great deal.

211
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:02,030
Chief Lu's bloodlust knows no bounds,

212
00:14:02,030 --> 00:14:03,690
yet the sect leader obeys him.

213
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:05,190
I'll never support this.

214
00:14:05,190 --> 00:14:06,530
I heard from Murong Xuan of Yanmen

215
00:14:06,530 --> 00:14:08,870
the Six Harmonies Divine Art was created
by the ancestors of Shengyue Sect.

216
00:14:08,870 --> 00:14:10,080
It's ruthless and vicious,

217
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:12,960
turning practitioners bloodthirsty enough
to turn against their own family.

218
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:15,440
Chief Lu is obsessed
with destroying Shengyue Sect,

219
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:17,120
probably because he's worried
that since the Six Harmonies Divine Art

220
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:18,630
was originally created
by someone from Shengyue Sect,

221
00:14:18,630 --> 00:14:20,870
they might still have
some records of the technique.

222
00:14:20,870 --> 00:14:22,270
Only by eliminating Shengyue Sect

223
00:14:22,270 --> 00:14:24,470
can he secure his invincible position.

224
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:26,280
A hundred years ago,
Yunmen's founding master

225
00:14:26,280 --> 00:14:27,670
once found a way to counter this skill.

226
00:14:27,670 --> 00:14:29,470
Do you know anything about that?

227
00:14:29,690 --> 00:14:30,810
I only heard

228
00:14:31,430 --> 00:14:33,330
our founding master
used the Alliance Leader's Token,

229
00:14:33,330 --> 00:14:35,130
the Sun and Moon Blades,
to defeat the enemy.

230
00:14:35,130 --> 00:14:38,130
But... I've returned the Sun Blade
to the sect leader.

231
00:14:38,760 --> 00:14:40,960
I'm afraid it's now in Chief Lu's hands.

232
00:14:41,010 --> 00:14:43,010
The Sun Blade I handed over was fake.

233
00:14:43,330 --> 00:14:45,040
I'll take care of the Sun and Moon Blades.

234
00:14:45,040 --> 00:14:47,000
Lu Jin has become a great threat
to the martial world.

235
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:48,600
If the martial world falls into his hands,

236
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:49,870
the consequences would be unimaginable.

237
00:14:49,870 --> 00:14:51,030
We must stop him quickly.

238
00:14:51,030 --> 00:14:51,490
Come on.

239
00:14:51,600 --> 00:14:52,800
Let's leave quickly.

240
00:14:57,750 --> 00:15:01,630
I was wondering
what rat snuck into Seclusion Valley.

241
00:15:02,910 --> 00:15:05,910
This truly proves
that no matter how vigilant you are,

242
00:15:07,100 --> 00:15:09,430
you can't guard against the enemy within.

243
00:15:09,510 --> 00:15:11,320
Wang Yuanhao,

244
00:15:12,050 --> 00:15:14,240
I've always known you're a hypocrite.

245
00:15:14,450 --> 00:15:16,180
Your surrender was just an act.

246
00:15:16,870 --> 00:15:19,630
Now, you're trying
to help Yang Qing escape,

247
00:15:19,740 --> 00:15:21,540
and I've caught you red-handed.

248
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:22,480
What else

249
00:15:23,240 --> 00:15:24,870
do you have to say?

250
00:15:25,760 --> 00:15:26,300
Junior Yang,

251
00:15:26,300 --> 00:15:27,230
you leave first.

252
00:15:28,100 --> 00:15:29,310
I have nothing to say!

253
00:15:29,790 --> 00:15:31,250
Those who harm the people—

254
00:15:31,450 --> 00:15:33,380
anybody has the right to kill them!

255
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:15,750
Qing,

256
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:17,050
take this scroll

257
00:16:17,150 --> 00:16:17,750
and leave!

258
00:16:18,940 --> 00:16:19,890
Feng Xingyun,

259
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:21,350
don't forget

260
00:16:21,950 --> 00:16:24,210
you were struck by my Six Harmonies Palm.

261
00:16:24,450 --> 00:16:26,240
Without me
transferring inner strength to you,

262
00:16:26,240 --> 00:16:27,570
you will certainly die!

263
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:29,960
I, Feng Xingyun,

264
00:16:30,390 --> 00:16:31,600
would never stoop

265
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:33,340
to colluding with a scumbag like you
who's been practicing

266
00:16:33,340 --> 00:16:35,270
the evil Six Harmonies Divine Art!

267
00:16:35,910 --> 00:16:36,480
Qing,

268
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:40,000
Lu Jin has mastered
the evil Six Harmonies Divine Art.

269
00:16:40,150 --> 00:16:42,750
The way to break it is on the scroll.

270
00:16:43,550 --> 00:16:44,150
Remember,

271
00:16:44,480 --> 00:16:46,040
Lu Jin must be killed!

272
00:16:47,520 --> 00:16:47,970
Leave!

273
00:17:28,390 --> 00:17:29,520
Yunmen's disciples

274
00:17:29,550 --> 00:17:30,860
would rather break than bend.

275
00:17:30,860 --> 00:17:33,200
We should make it our duty
to help the people.

276
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:34,410
We practice martial arts

277
00:17:34,410 --> 00:17:36,110
only to save people from suffering

278
00:17:36,110 --> 00:17:37,590
and fight against injustice.

279
00:17:37,590 --> 00:17:38,110
Got it.

280
00:18:07,280 --> 00:18:10,670
[Yunmen]

281
00:18:11,410 --> 00:18:13,910
I've gathered you all here today

282
00:18:15,170 --> 00:18:17,570
because I have important news to announce.

283
00:18:18,490 --> 00:18:21,290
Yang Qing has betrayed us
by joining Shengyue Sect

284
00:18:21,440 --> 00:18:24,320
and personally killed his master
and Elder Wang.

285
00:18:24,350 --> 00:18:25,160
How is that possible?

286
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:26,350
-It can't be true.
-Yeah.

287
00:18:26,350 --> 00:18:27,070
How is that possible?

288
00:18:27,070 --> 00:18:28,310
How is that possible?

289
00:18:29,510 --> 00:18:31,190
I have both witnesses and evidence!

290
00:18:31,190 --> 00:18:32,590
What else is there to say?

291
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:34,680
This is indeed Mr. Yang's sword,

292
00:18:34,790 --> 00:18:36,380
but based on just a sword alone,

293
00:18:36,380 --> 00:18:38,100
how can you be sure
that Mr. Yang is the killer?

294
00:18:38,100 --> 00:18:40,550
-That's right!
-That's right!

295
00:18:40,880 --> 00:18:41,590
Chief Lu,

296
00:18:41,680 --> 00:18:44,270
don't you think
you're making a hasty judgment?

297
00:18:44,270 --> 00:18:45,000
That's right.

298
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:47,110
God knows if you took his sword yourself.

299
00:18:47,110 --> 00:18:47,680
Chief Lu,

300
00:18:48,030 --> 00:18:49,320
murder is a serious crime.

301
00:18:49,320 --> 00:18:50,550
Drawing a conclusion so hastily...

302
00:18:50,550 --> 00:18:51,830
Stop arguing!

303
00:18:51,930 --> 00:18:53,530
You're giving me a headache!

304
00:18:53,880 --> 00:18:54,340
This...

305
00:18:57,590 --> 00:19:01,240
You people from Yunmen are defending
Yang Qing!

306
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:03,600
Are you his accomplices?

307
00:19:03,920 --> 00:19:04,270
Yeah.

308
00:19:04,600 --> 00:19:05,830
So what if we are?

309
00:19:05,850 --> 00:19:08,010
I asked you guys here today

310
00:19:09,940 --> 00:19:11,220
to call upon all of you

311
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:14,160
to join Biluo Valley
in eliminating the evil!

312
00:19:16,680 --> 00:19:19,560
Yunmen can't even properly manage

313
00:19:19,590 --> 00:19:20,990
its own internal affairs.

314
00:19:20,990 --> 00:19:24,320
And it even has a traitor
who's colluded with Shengyue Sect!

315
00:19:24,830 --> 00:19:28,230
Naturally, Biluo Valley
should take on this responsibility

316
00:19:28,790 --> 00:19:30,390
to eliminate Shengyue Sect.

317
00:19:31,270 --> 00:19:32,180
Only then...

318
00:19:35,790 --> 00:19:38,230
Only then can the world be at peace.

319
00:19:45,880 --> 00:19:46,830
[Wangyou Pavilion]

320
00:19:46,830 --> 00:19:47,360
Go ahead.

321
00:19:47,860 --> 00:19:49,130
What's the situation now?

322
00:19:49,130 --> 00:19:51,580
The sect leader
and Senior Wang were killed

323
00:19:53,020 --> 00:19:54,820
by Lu Jin while trying to save me.

324
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:04,880
This...

325
00:20:09,110 --> 00:20:10,240
It's not your fault.

326
00:20:11,170 --> 00:20:12,300
It's not your fault.

327
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:14,810
No one could have imagined

328
00:20:15,070 --> 00:20:17,570
that Lu Jin would have
such treacherous ambition,

329
00:20:17,570 --> 00:20:19,770
willing to practice the evil technique

330
00:20:20,070 --> 00:20:22,070
just to dominate the martial world.

331
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:24,680
Go on.

332
00:20:25,880 --> 00:20:27,540
Lu Jin framed me for the deaths

333
00:20:28,180 --> 00:20:30,110
of the sect leader and Senior Wang,

334
00:20:30,110 --> 00:20:33,240
led Biluo Valley's disciples
to take control of Yunmen,

335
00:20:33,310 --> 00:20:36,170
and tricked the other sects
into allying with them.

336
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:38,940
They plan to destroy Shengyue Sect soon.

337
00:20:41,650 --> 00:20:44,340
This puts us at a severe disadvantage.

338
00:20:46,020 --> 00:20:47,350
Is there no way to get

339
00:20:47,660 --> 00:20:49,660
the other sects to stand on our side?

340
00:20:49,780 --> 00:20:50,520
I still don't have the evidence

341
00:20:50,520 --> 00:20:52,480
to prove
Lu Jin is practicing the evil technique,

342
00:20:52,480 --> 00:20:55,340
so it's very hard
to make the other sects believe us.

343
00:20:57,200 --> 00:20:58,460
But it doesn't matter.

344
00:20:58,490 --> 00:21:00,220
I've already found a solution.

345
00:21:00,640 --> 00:21:02,150
As long as we
break the Six Harmonies Divine Art,

346
00:21:02,150 --> 00:21:04,280
the other sects will naturally see

347
00:21:04,350 --> 00:21:05,550
Lu Jin's true colors.

348
00:21:09,210 --> 00:21:09,670
Junior,

349
00:21:10,550 --> 00:21:12,150
the Six Harmonies Divine Art

350
00:21:12,160 --> 00:21:14,750
isn't something
that can be easily dealt with.

351
00:21:14,750 --> 00:21:16,590
Right now, it's just the few of us.

352
00:21:16,590 --> 00:21:20,010
It won't be easy to fight against
Biluo Valley's overwhelming forces.

353
00:21:20,010 --> 00:21:21,950
Yuan Yingxing has agreed
to join forces with us.

354
00:21:21,950 --> 00:21:23,480
We won't be fighting alone.

355
00:21:25,140 --> 00:21:26,340
Senior, don't worry.

356
00:21:27,600 --> 00:21:30,190
I won't let
the sect leader and Senior Wang

357
00:21:31,510 --> 00:21:32,200
die in vain.

358
00:21:34,070 --> 00:21:34,600
Mr. Shen,

359
00:21:35,270 --> 00:21:37,200
evil can never prevail over righteousness.

360
00:21:37,200 --> 00:21:39,000
At worst, we'll fight to the end!

361
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:39,790
Yes.

362
00:21:40,220 --> 00:21:41,150
Fight to the end.

363
00:21:41,180 --> 00:21:42,150
We can do this!

364
00:21:58,970 --> 00:21:59,050
The chief of Biluo Valley

365
00:21:59,050 --> 00:22:00,060
[Tianyu Palace]

366
00:22:00,060 --> 00:22:01,890
is leading all sects to surround us
at the foot of the mountain,

367
00:22:01,890 --> 00:22:03,350
demanding our surrender.

368
00:22:03,350 --> 00:22:03,920
I see.

369
00:22:04,440 --> 00:22:05,920
Keep watching them down the mountain.

370
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:06,480
Yes.

371
00:22:06,880 --> 00:22:08,650
I didn't expect them to come so soon.

372
00:22:08,650 --> 00:22:10,380
I thought we had a few more days.

373
00:22:10,920 --> 00:22:11,580
Chief Yuan.

374
00:22:12,020 --> 00:22:12,550
Lingyin,

375
00:22:13,130 --> 00:22:14,480
keep a close eye on the saintess.

376
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:15,740
I'll go deal with them.

377
00:22:16,550 --> 00:22:17,350
Yes, Chief.

378
00:22:27,480 --> 00:22:30,330
Will Yuan Yingxing surrender or not?

379
00:22:31,350 --> 00:22:32,240
Father,

380
00:22:32,400 --> 00:22:33,800
there's no response yet.

381
00:22:39,300 --> 00:22:41,580
Petty Shengyue Sect.

382
00:22:42,240 --> 00:22:43,240
He won't come out?

383
00:22:44,830 --> 00:22:47,560
Does he really think
I have no way to deal with him?

384
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:50,030
Guards.

385
00:22:55,000 --> 00:22:55,530
Chief Lu,

386
00:22:55,690 --> 00:22:57,020
what are you going to do?

387
00:22:57,310 --> 00:22:57,910
Pour oil.

388
00:22:58,680 --> 00:23:00,220
Set the mountain on fire.

389
00:23:00,580 --> 00:23:04,830
[Shengyue Sect]

390
00:23:16,070 --> 00:23:17,830
So the righteous Biluo Valley

391
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:21,280
has resorted
to such despicable tactics as arson?

392
00:23:23,750 --> 00:23:24,200
Lu Jin,

393
00:23:24,750 --> 00:23:26,460
you've been practicing
the Six Harmonies Divine Art.

394
00:23:26,460 --> 00:23:28,260
You think you can keep it hidden?

395
00:23:31,110 --> 00:23:33,200
Many people in Biluo Valley died suddenly.

396
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:34,680
Can you explain that

397
00:23:35,120 --> 00:23:36,850
in front of all the other sects?

398
00:23:38,640 --> 00:23:39,570
A few months ago,

399
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:42,030
the missing children case in Yangliu Town

400
00:23:42,030 --> 00:23:44,030
and the rove beetles in Yunyin Village—

401
00:23:44,030 --> 00:23:46,030
Miss Lu, do you dare say those things

402
00:23:46,290 --> 00:23:48,350
have nothing to do with Biluo Valley?

403
00:23:48,880 --> 00:23:49,440
I...

404
00:23:53,040 --> 00:23:54,690
Chief Lu has been practicing
an evil technique.

405
00:23:54,690 --> 00:23:55,960
He's changed completely,

406
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:57,270
confusing right and wrong

407
00:23:57,270 --> 00:23:59,000
and harming the martial world.

408
00:23:59,710 --> 00:24:00,820
That kind of evil technique—

409
00:24:00,820 --> 00:24:03,080
who else but you could have conceived it?

410
00:24:10,460 --> 00:24:13,290
You demon, you're slandering me!

411
00:24:15,000 --> 00:24:15,790
Yang Qing,

412
00:24:16,960 --> 00:24:18,850
you betrayed us and joined the evil sect.

413
00:24:18,850 --> 00:24:22,050
You killed your master, Sect Leader Feng,
and Elder Wang.

414
00:24:22,490 --> 00:24:25,420
And now you're helping this demon
falsely accuse me!

415
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:27,550
Fellow heroes!

416
00:24:28,590 --> 00:24:30,830
Don't listen to his slanderous lies!

417
00:24:31,510 --> 00:24:32,370
Kill Yang Qing,

418
00:24:32,670 --> 00:24:34,070
avenge Sect Leader Feng,

419
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:35,970
destroy Shengyue Sect,

420
00:24:36,070 --> 00:24:37,680
and restore the world to peace!

421
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:44,480
Kill! Kill! Kill!

422
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:45,750
Lu Jin,

423
00:24:46,870 --> 00:24:48,110
stop.

424
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:50,130
Stop harming innocent people.

425
00:24:51,000 --> 00:24:52,570
Isn't that... Isn't that Murong Xuan?

426
00:24:52,570 --> 00:24:53,820
Yes, Murong Xuan.

427
00:24:53,870 --> 00:24:54,870
Murong Xuan?

428
00:24:57,650 --> 00:25:00,480
So, you still remember me.

429
00:25:02,140 --> 00:25:04,000
Then you must also remember this.

430
00:25:04,580 --> 00:25:08,240
Back then, I tried to stop you
from practicing the evil technique,

431
00:25:08,510 --> 00:25:10,510
so you destroyed Yanmen in revenge,

432
00:25:10,600 --> 00:25:13,270
forcing me to flee
with the few surviving disciples

433
00:25:13,270 --> 00:25:14,380
to Mount Yin!

434
00:25:15,820 --> 00:25:16,550
Is that true?

435
00:25:17,130 --> 00:25:18,590
You're talking nonsense!

436
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:19,720
Nonsense?

437
00:25:21,440 --> 00:25:22,150
Lu Jin,

438
00:25:22,680 --> 00:25:25,640
do you know that practicing
the Six Harmonies Divine Art

439
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:27,480
causes black veins to appear?

440
00:25:28,790 --> 00:25:30,000
If you have nothing to hide,

441
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:31,200
take off your clothes

442
00:25:31,410 --> 00:25:33,340
and let everyone here see

443
00:25:33,920 --> 00:25:35,920
whether you've practiced it or not.

444
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:42,590
I'm the chief of Biluo Valley

445
00:25:43,220 --> 00:25:45,020
and the acting alliance leader!

446
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:46,760
Taking off clothes in public

447
00:25:47,310 --> 00:25:48,550
would be utterly inappropriate!

448
00:25:48,550 --> 00:25:49,350
That's right.

449
00:25:50,440 --> 00:25:51,200
Chief Lu,

450
00:25:51,790 --> 00:25:53,270
if you don't dare to do this,
just say so.

451
00:25:53,270 --> 00:25:54,400
Don't make excuses.

452
00:25:54,830 --> 00:25:55,360
Chief Lu,

453
00:25:55,530 --> 00:25:57,320
take off your clothes and show them!

454
00:25:57,320 --> 00:25:59,830
After all, it's a minor faction
that has joined the evil sect.

455
00:25:59,830 --> 00:26:02,510
How dare they accuse the Central Plains martial world
of practicing an evil technique.

456
00:26:02,510 --> 00:26:03,850
I don't believe his nonsense.

457
00:26:03,850 --> 00:26:05,000
Chief Lu, show him!

458
00:26:05,030 --> 00:26:06,160
Show him! Take off your clothes!

459
00:26:06,160 --> 00:26:07,240
He's a mere traitor!

460
00:26:07,240 --> 00:26:09,040
How can you believe what he said?

461
00:26:09,270 --> 00:26:10,730
He's trying to sow discord

462
00:26:10,830 --> 00:26:12,090
and damage our morale!

463
00:26:16,440 --> 00:26:17,300
Master Murong.

464
00:26:18,680 --> 00:26:19,540
Master Murong.

465
00:26:24,340 --> 00:26:25,140
From today on,

466
00:26:25,950 --> 00:26:29,470
I'll be the alliance leader!

467
00:26:30,160 --> 00:26:32,960
And Biluo Valley
will dominate the martial world!

468
00:26:34,020 --> 00:26:36,620
Those who defy me
will be killed without mercy!

469
00:26:39,680 --> 00:26:42,010
Did you hear the alliance leader clearly?

470
00:26:42,510 --> 00:26:44,240
Is there anyone not convinced?

471
00:26:46,480 --> 00:26:47,540
I'm not convinced!

472
00:26:52,550 --> 00:26:54,010
Who else is not convinced?

473
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:54,920
Lu Jin!

474
00:26:55,400 --> 00:26:56,400
You've gone mad!

475
00:26:56,790 --> 00:26:58,710
You want Qingcheng Sect
to submit to a demon like you?

476
00:26:58,710 --> 00:26:59,510
Never!

477
00:26:59,880 --> 00:27:01,140
Today, Qingcheng Sect

478
00:27:01,660 --> 00:27:03,510
is going to eliminate the evil
and uphold justice for the people!

479
00:27:03,510 --> 00:27:04,200
Kill!

480
00:27:04,360 --> 00:27:05,120
Stop!

481
00:27:15,480 --> 00:27:16,280
Xuanxuan!

482
00:27:37,930 --> 00:27:38,460
Lingyin!

483
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:39,550
Chief!

484
00:27:39,760 --> 00:27:40,270
Chief Yuan.

485
00:27:40,270 --> 00:27:41,000
Don't speak.

486
00:27:41,130 --> 00:27:42,150
Hurry! Check on him!

487
00:27:42,150 --> 00:27:42,630
Yes.

488
00:27:45,720 --> 00:27:46,640
Chief Yuan.

489
00:27:48,560 --> 00:27:50,890
Chief Lu has mastered the evil technique.

490
00:27:52,520 --> 00:27:55,250
With that strike from him,

491
00:27:56,340 --> 00:27:57,940
I have no more than 45 minutes

492
00:27:59,030 --> 00:28:00,590
before I die.

493
00:28:00,980 --> 00:28:01,710
Impossible!

494
00:28:05,110 --> 00:28:05,960
Chief Yuan.

495
00:28:07,440 --> 00:28:11,350
Actually, you're a good chief.

496
00:28:13,960 --> 00:28:15,240
Don't let Lu Jin...

497
00:28:15,720 --> 00:28:18,070
harm anyone anymore.

498
00:28:18,240 --> 00:28:19,070
Master Murong.

499
00:28:19,070 --> 00:28:19,930
Master Murong!

500
00:28:20,590 --> 00:28:21,450
Yuan Yingxing,

501
00:28:21,640 --> 00:28:23,440
go get the Sun and Moon Blades now

502
00:28:23,820 --> 00:28:25,550
to break
Lu Jin's Six Harmonies Divine Art.

503
00:28:25,550 --> 00:28:27,750
Then let's see how arrogant he remains.

504
00:28:36,380 --> 00:28:39,250
I heard Biluo Valley has sent people
to surround Mount Yin.

505
00:28:39,250 --> 00:28:40,910
You just focus on recovering.

506
00:28:41,010 --> 00:28:42,390
Petty Biluo Valley is

507
00:28:42,530 --> 00:28:43,460
nothing to fear.

508
00:28:43,900 --> 00:28:45,300
Then why are you here now?

509
00:28:46,970 --> 00:28:47,700
I missed you,

510
00:28:48,060 --> 00:28:49,390
so I came to check on you.

511
00:28:52,410 --> 00:28:54,330
Are you... leaving soon?

512
00:28:59,240 --> 00:29:01,700
What if I take the Sun and Moon Blades
by force

513
00:29:02,170 --> 00:29:03,300
to make you stay?

514
00:29:04,550 --> 00:29:05,840
You know I can't stay.

515
00:29:07,110 --> 00:29:09,820
If I stay here, I'm as good as dead.

516
00:29:17,330 --> 00:29:18,190
Then promise me

517
00:29:18,580 --> 00:29:20,110
that no matter where you go,

518
00:29:20,590 --> 00:29:21,720
you won't forget me.

519
00:29:23,750 --> 00:29:24,400
Yingxing,

520
00:29:25,830 --> 00:29:27,690
are you hiding something from me?

521
00:29:29,110 --> 00:29:29,870
No.

522
00:29:31,010 --> 00:29:31,490
Say it—

523
00:29:32,750 --> 00:29:34,080
you'll never forget me.

524
00:29:34,830 --> 00:29:35,270
Okay.

525
00:29:36,720 --> 00:29:37,450
Pinky swear.

526
00:29:45,320 --> 00:29:46,650
I will never forget you.

527
00:29:54,030 --> 00:29:54,580
So?

528
00:29:56,530 --> 00:29:57,480
I will kill Lu Jin

529
00:29:57,800 --> 00:29:59,330
and give everyone closure.

530
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:07,060
Did he mean
he didn't get the Sun and Moon Blades?

531
00:30:08,980 --> 00:30:11,510
It must be
because of that wicked woman again.

532
00:30:11,660 --> 00:30:12,950
Giving us closure?

533
00:30:13,100 --> 00:30:13,890
How exactly?

534
00:30:14,510 --> 00:30:15,110
Forget it.

535
00:30:15,110 --> 00:30:15,900
Let's go find Yao Fu.

536
00:30:15,900 --> 00:30:16,430
Let's go.

537
00:30:19,830 --> 00:30:20,960
Where are you going?

538
00:30:23,030 --> 00:30:24,960
Has Yuan Yingxing changed his mind?

539
00:30:24,960 --> 00:30:27,610
So he asked you
to take back the Sun and Moon Blades?

540
00:30:27,610 --> 00:30:29,270
I wish he had changed his mind,

541
00:30:29,400 --> 00:30:31,270
but he'd rather sacrifice himself

542
00:30:31,270 --> 00:30:33,070
than let anything happen to you.

543
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:35,050
Let's put aside our grudges for now.

544
00:30:35,050 --> 00:30:35,610
But

545
00:30:36,070 --> 00:30:38,200
do you have the heart
to let him die for you?

546
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:39,130
What did you say?

547
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:41,060
Lu Jin has mastered the evil technique.

548
00:30:41,060 --> 00:30:42,130
Now, only the Sun and Moon Blades

549
00:30:42,130 --> 00:30:43,260
can break it.

550
00:30:43,630 --> 00:30:44,150
But...

551
00:30:44,500 --> 00:30:46,600
he said the blades are crucial
to your safety

552
00:30:46,600 --> 00:30:48,130
and you'd die without them.

553
00:30:48,790 --> 00:30:49,520
So he gave up.

554
00:30:51,030 --> 00:30:53,420
Chief has never changed his mind,

555
00:30:54,070 --> 00:30:56,520
because he's gone down the mountain
to his death.

556
00:30:56,520 --> 00:30:58,580
How can a dead man change his mind?

557
00:31:41,960 --> 00:31:42,670
Yingxing!

558
00:31:43,120 --> 00:31:44,650
Yingxing, are you alright?

559
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:46,110
You're such a fool!

560
00:31:47,080 --> 00:31:48,110
If I hadn't come,

561
00:31:48,940 --> 00:31:50,750
would you really die for me willingly?

562
00:31:50,750 --> 00:31:51,240
Yao.

563
00:31:52,270 --> 00:31:53,720
Why did you come?

564
00:31:53,840 --> 00:31:55,370
Didn't I tell you to go back?

565
00:31:55,590 --> 00:31:56,530
Just wait a little longer.

566
00:31:56,530 --> 00:31:57,930
After they defeat Lu Jin,

567
00:31:57,960 --> 00:32:00,290
I'll get you the Alliance Leader's Token.

568
00:32:03,680 --> 00:32:04,680
No.

569
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:06,640
The martial world is in such chaos.

570
00:32:06,640 --> 00:32:09,110
Yang Qing may not be able to restore order
without the Alliance Leader's Token.

571
00:32:09,110 --> 00:32:10,400
Why should I care about the martial world?

572
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:11,340
I only want you.

573
00:32:11,360 --> 00:32:14,600
Yingxing, I don't have much time left.

574
00:32:15,080 --> 00:32:16,200
Let me go.

575
00:32:17,030 --> 00:32:19,510
I don't want you to see me dying.

576
00:32:20,610 --> 00:32:22,140
Take good care of yourself.

577
00:32:24,120 --> 00:32:25,780
-Remember our promise.
-Yao.

578
00:32:26,160 --> 00:32:27,510
I won't let you die.

579
00:32:27,960 --> 00:32:29,000
You'll be fine.

580
00:32:29,510 --> 00:32:30,000
Yao.

581
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:43,700
♪ Good and evil are irreconcilable,
it's predestined ♪

582
00:32:43,730 --> 00:32:46,270
♪ You deliberately disturbed my heart ♪

583
00:32:47,020 --> 00:32:50,540
♪ There are numerous
unsolved mysteries in the world ♪

584
00:32:50,800 --> 00:32:53,420
♪ You are the most difficult one ♪

585
00:32:54,120 --> 00:32:56,790
♪ The road is rugged,
I'll go against the wind ♪

586
00:32:56,820 --> 00:32:59,820
♪ I woke up from my dream ♪

587
00:33:00,110 --> 00:33:03,910
♪ The tears falling from your eyes ♪

588
00:33:03,950 --> 00:33:06,610
♪ In the vague shadow ♪

589
00:33:07,130 --> 00:33:13,460
♪ I see myself ♪

590
00:33:13,480 --> 00:33:17,750
♪ The shining stars, the soft waves ♪

591
00:33:18,000 --> 00:33:20,510
♪ The martial world is at peace now ♪

592
00:33:20,740 --> 00:33:23,630
♪ This is the battlefield you expect ♪

593
00:33:23,810 --> 00:33:27,140
♪ Only through pain comes forgiveness ♪

594
00:33:27,300 --> 00:33:30,890
♪ The scorching sun is admired by all ♪

595
00:33:31,160 --> 00:33:34,070
♪ The martial world is at peace ♪

596
00:33:34,320 --> 00:33:37,320
♪ You keep my mind at peace ♪

597
00:33:37,740 --> 00:33:40,240
♪ Till the end of the world ♪

598
00:33:40,260 --> 00:33:43,770
♪ Never despair ♪

599
00:33:47,330 --> 00:33:52,280
♪ Never look back ♪

600
00:33:55,860 --> 00:33:57,370
How could I die?

601
00:34:09,190 --> 00:34:10,110
Great.

602
00:34:29,420 --> 00:34:32,480
[Yunmen]

603
00:35:13,900 --> 00:35:16,860
The Biluo Valley incident
has a far-reaching influence.

604
00:35:16,860 --> 00:35:18,450
In the Central Plains martial world,

605
00:35:18,450 --> 00:35:20,760
not everyone is righteous or chivalrous.

606
00:35:20,760 --> 00:35:22,560
And the so-called Shengyue Sect

607
00:35:22,580 --> 00:35:25,440
is certainly not
a group of unforgivable villains.

608
00:35:25,630 --> 00:35:26,470
From now on,

609
00:35:27,070 --> 00:35:30,490
Yunmen and Shengyue Sect will be allies
for generations to come,

610
00:35:30,490 --> 00:35:31,550
living in harmony,

611
00:35:32,170 --> 00:35:33,090
no more strife!

612
00:35:33,810 --> 00:35:37,410
-You're wise, Alliance Leader!
-You're wise, Alliance Leader!

613
00:35:40,630 --> 00:35:43,440
[Tianyu Palace]

614
00:35:44,370 --> 00:35:46,170
A letter for you from Chief Yuan.

615
00:35:50,230 --> 00:35:51,190
Lu Jin is dead.

616
00:35:52,030 --> 00:35:54,130
Shengyue Sect has made up
with the martial world.

617
00:35:54,130 --> 00:35:55,590
With Yang Qing's support,

618
00:35:55,760 --> 00:35:56,930
there should be no worries.

619
00:35:56,930 --> 00:35:57,390
Don't worry about me.

620
00:35:57,390 --> 00:35:58,660
Yuan Yingxing!

621
00:36:00,090 --> 00:36:01,380
What's going on?

622
00:36:02,820 --> 00:36:03,840
He said he's too tired

623
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:04,670
and he's leaving.

624
00:36:04,670 --> 00:36:07,130
He'll just
abandon Shengyue Sect like this.

625
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:10,670
It must be because of Yao Fu again.

626
00:36:11,670 --> 00:36:12,640
Chief

627
00:36:12,670 --> 00:36:14,400
really is an affectionate man.

628
00:36:16,050 --> 00:36:16,760
Lingyin.

629
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:18,290
My Water Hall Master,

630
00:36:18,290 --> 00:36:19,360
you can't leave.

631
00:36:19,760 --> 00:36:20,730
If you leave,

632
00:36:20,760 --> 00:36:23,490
there will be no one
to manage the sect's affairs.

633
00:36:23,920 --> 00:36:25,880
I... I don't want to.

634
00:36:26,350 --> 00:36:28,330
I've already promised Mingyang

635
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:29,760
to travel around the world together.

636
00:36:29,760 --> 00:36:30,590
What?

637
00:36:31,260 --> 00:36:32,950
When did you two get together?

638
00:36:33,590 --> 00:36:34,710
If you guys leave,

639
00:36:35,380 --> 00:36:37,640
there'll be no one else in Shengyue Sect.

640
00:36:38,030 --> 00:36:39,030
No one else?

641
00:36:40,190 --> 00:36:41,650
What about your Yang Qing?

642
00:36:42,480 --> 00:36:44,840
With him helping manage Shengyue Sect,

643
00:36:44,920 --> 00:36:47,320
I think
he'd be much more reliable than you.

644
00:36:47,800 --> 00:36:48,480
Him?

645
00:36:48,910 --> 00:36:50,370
He's planning to marry me.

646
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:51,780
Last time, he took me as his bride.

647
00:36:51,780 --> 00:36:53,580
This time, I'll take him as mine.

648
00:36:53,760 --> 00:36:54,360
By the way,

649
00:36:54,590 --> 00:36:56,190
the wedding will be held right here.

650
00:36:56,190 --> 00:36:58,720
Everyone from Yunmen
will come to celebrate.

651
00:37:02,840 --> 00:37:05,750
[Tianyu Palace]

652
00:37:18,210 --> 00:37:23,210
♪ Time flows like sand in an hourglass,
counting down to forever ♪

653
00:37:24,480 --> 00:37:29,870
♪ Only at the moment we met did I learn
what pain and sorrow truly are ♪

654
00:37:31,450 --> 00:37:34,450
♪ The cold wind softens little by little ♪

655
00:37:34,970 --> 00:37:43,680
♪ Though carefree, I can't resist the gaze
written in my fate ♪

656
00:37:44,380 --> 00:37:47,150
♪ I remember the old days,
forgetting all past grudges ♪

657
00:37:47,150 --> 00:37:48,610
My Yue is truly beautiful.

658
00:37:50,400 --> 00:37:50,990
Jealous, huh?

659
00:37:50,990 --> 00:37:56,420
♪ Through the rise and fall
of the world's cruel game ♪

660
00:37:57,360 --> 00:38:00,810
♪ I cherish your gentle touch ♪

661
00:38:01,310 --> 00:38:06,340
♪ The long, winding road
lingers in my heart ♪

662
00:38:06,540 --> 00:38:09,660
♪ Like dark clouds surging ♪

663
00:38:10,860 --> 00:38:14,630
♪ I vow my life, giving all I have ♪

664
00:38:14,660 --> 00:38:17,080
♪ Betting on a timeless promise ♪

665
00:38:17,320 --> 00:38:17,960
♪ Holding you despite tremendous danger ♪

666
00:38:17,960 --> 00:38:18,510
Today,

667
00:38:18,800 --> 00:38:22,480
Yang Qing and Wang Yue are joined
in matrimony,

668
00:38:23,070 --> 00:38:23,620
a perfect match,

669
00:38:23,620 --> 00:38:24,750
♪ Unraveling the conspiracy of time ♪

670
00:38:24,750 --> 00:38:26,080
a bond forever.

671
00:38:26,780 --> 00:38:27,610
The bride and groom, before the hall,

672
00:38:27,610 --> 00:38:29,740
♪ Holding your hand ♪

673
00:38:29,770 --> 00:38:29,800
♪ I walk with you
through countless mountains and rivers ♪

674
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:31,930
make the first bow to heaven and earth!

675
00:38:49,000 --> 00:38:51,190
Make the second bow to parents!

676
00:38:56,020 --> 00:39:01,140
♪ I remember the old days,
forgetting all past grudges ♪

677
00:39:02,580 --> 00:39:08,120
♪ Through the rise and fall
of the world's cruel game ♪

678
00:39:08,290 --> 00:39:09,410
Bow to each other!

679
00:39:09,410 --> 00:39:12,620
♪ I cherish your gentle touch ♪

680
00:39:13,110 --> 00:39:17,380
♪ The long, winding road
lingers in my heart ♪

681
00:39:18,360 --> 00:39:21,820
♪ Like dark clouds surging ♪

682
00:39:22,070 --> 00:39:22,710
♪ I vow never to look back
for the rest of my life ♪

683
00:39:22,710 --> 00:39:24,630
The ceremony is complete!

684
00:39:24,650 --> 00:39:25,910
-Great!
-Great!

685
00:39:25,910 --> 00:39:28,390
♪ Betting on forever ♪

686
00:39:28,750 --> 00:39:30,590
♪ I dare to let go of right and wrong ♪

687
00:39:30,610 --> 00:39:35,010
♪ Stay by your side ♪

688
00:39:35,150 --> 00:39:38,610
♪ Unafraid of hardships
or raging torrents ♪

689
00:39:39,090 --> 00:39:40,990
♪ I see longing with new clarity ♪

690
00:39:41,010 --> 00:39:48,010
♪ Love can heal all pain ♪

691
00:40:12,190 --> 00:40:14,320
Isn't this the novel I wrote years ago?

692
00:40:15,320 --> 00:40:16,280
Why is it here?

693
00:40:16,800 --> 00:40:19,070
Come take a look, everyone!

694
00:40:20,840 --> 00:40:23,010
The romantic story
between Shengyue Sect's saintess

695
00:40:23,010 --> 00:40:24,170
and Yang Qing from Yunmen.

696
00:40:24,170 --> 00:40:25,830
A new volume is now available!

697
00:40:25,840 --> 00:40:26,630
Don't push!

698
00:40:26,770 --> 00:40:27,670
Don't be anxious!

699
00:40:27,670 --> 00:40:28,730
Everyone, line up!

700
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:29,540
One at a time.

701
00:40:29,590 --> 00:40:29,740
Here.

702
00:40:29,740 --> 00:40:30,550
[How I Got My Husband]

703
00:40:30,550 --> 00:40:31,150
Line up.

704
00:40:31,320 --> 00:40:32,400
There's enough for everyone!

705
00:40:32,400 --> 00:40:33,400
Don't be anxious!

706
00:40:34,150 --> 00:40:35,000
Here you go.

707
00:40:35,320 --> 00:40:36,150
Sir,

708
00:40:36,350 --> 00:40:37,560
nice grab there.

709
00:40:37,690 --> 00:40:38,800
You're the first one.

710
00:40:38,800 --> 00:40:41,230
Would you like me to sign on your copy?

711
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:46,670
This is too little.

712
00:40:47,020 --> 00:40:48,520
For this tiny amount of money,

713
00:40:48,520 --> 00:40:50,520
is selling books yourself worth it?

714
00:40:50,880 --> 00:40:52,140
You don't understand.

715
00:40:52,150 --> 00:40:53,630
I can't win Yang Qing's heart
in real life,

716
00:40:53,630 --> 00:40:55,180
so I wrote a novel about us.

717
00:40:55,530 --> 00:40:56,960
Then everyone in the world

718
00:40:56,960 --> 00:40:59,110
would marvel at our perfect love.

719
00:40:59,480 --> 00:41:01,960
That's practically the same
as winning his heart.

720
00:41:01,960 --> 00:41:02,820
In this volume,

721
00:41:03,100 --> 00:41:04,920
I've written
that the saintess and Yang Qing

722
00:41:04,920 --> 00:41:06,320
already have 3 children.

723
00:41:07,110 --> 00:41:07,760
Three...

724
00:41:08,780 --> 00:41:09,390
Yue,

725
00:41:10,100 --> 00:41:12,410
you two haven't even held hands,

726
00:41:12,530 --> 00:41:15,320
yet in your novel,
you already have 3 children?

727
00:41:17,760 --> 00:41:20,010
Yue, that's so you.

728
00:41:22,150 --> 00:41:22,880
Impressive.

729
00:41:30,240 --> 00:41:30,890
Wangyue.

730
00:41:34,870 --> 00:41:35,600
Wangyue!

731
00:41:40,800 --> 00:41:41,480
Wangyue.

732
00:41:42,770 --> 00:41:43,410
Tell me,

733
00:41:44,720 --> 00:41:47,210
is this the grand wedding you wanted?

734
00:41:51,590 --> 00:41:52,550
I will fulfill

735
00:41:54,070 --> 00:41:55,650
my promises to you.

736
00:41:56,530 --> 00:41:58,030
I will never go back on my word.

737
00:41:58,030 --> 00:41:58,780
Yang Qing.

738
00:42:00,030 --> 00:42:01,590
When I get married,

739
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:03,830
I'll make sure to invite everyone
in the world

740
00:42:03,830 --> 00:42:05,220
to my wedding.

741
00:42:05,760 --> 00:42:08,620
I'll send invitations to everyone
who dislikes me.

742
00:42:09,120 --> 00:42:10,870
I'll show off in front of them

743
00:42:11,070 --> 00:42:13,200
and make them give me their blessings.

744
00:42:13,710 --> 00:42:16,070
I'll spend a fortune on my wedding,

745
00:42:16,550 --> 00:42:18,210
becoming the most spectacular bride

746
00:42:18,210 --> 00:42:20,170
among all the saintesses.

747
00:42:21,070 --> 00:42:22,030
I won't

748
00:42:22,590 --> 00:42:23,960
get married secretly

749
00:42:24,440 --> 00:42:25,970
or just for my own pleasure.

750
00:42:26,270 --> 00:42:28,600
I want every single person
to give me a gift

751
00:42:28,630 --> 00:42:29,760
and bless me.

752
00:42:30,350 --> 00:42:31,510
Anyone who dares to defy me—

753
00:42:31,510 --> 00:42:32,510
I'll beat them up.

754
00:42:34,580 --> 00:42:36,510
I want a lavish display of flowers,

755
00:42:37,440 --> 00:42:39,300
hundreds of birds paying homage,

756
00:42:39,510 --> 00:42:41,110
and a grand turnout.

757
00:42:43,880 --> 00:42:44,550
Yang Qing.

758
00:42:46,400 --> 00:42:47,260
I didn't expect

759
00:42:48,030 --> 00:42:50,880
that everything I wrote in my novel
has come true.

760
00:42:55,480 --> 00:42:56,710
You're finally mine.

761
00:43:10,480 --> 00:43:11,030
Wangyue.

762
00:43:13,370 --> 00:43:16,760
You've finally become my wife.

763
00:43:19,230 --> 00:43:20,890
I've been waiting for this day

764
00:43:21,180 --> 00:43:22,350
for a very long time.

765
00:43:43,840 --> 00:43:44,510
Honey,

766
00:43:45,550 --> 00:43:48,910
shouldn't you explain

767
00:43:49,280 --> 00:43:50,610
why you have this novel?

768
00:43:58,250 --> 00:43:59,090
Actually...

769
00:43:59,960 --> 00:44:05,400
a very, very long time ago,

770
00:44:07,180 --> 00:44:08,840
I already liked you very much.

771
00:44:10,700 --> 00:44:11,540
But luckily,

772
00:44:12,930 --> 00:44:13,590
everything

773
00:44:14,960 --> 00:44:15,880
is still in time.
